com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.util

Class RowIdList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.util.RowIdList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<Integer>, Collection<Integer>, List<Integer>
    Deprecated. 
    No longer required as WDataTable is deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public final class RowIdList
extends Object
implements List<Integer>, Serializable

    This implementation of the List interface is not intended for general use, it exists solely to provide memory efficient support for WRepeater.getBeanList().

    This list is immutable; any attempts to call a mutator method will result in an UnsupportedOperationException being thrown.

    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Yiannis Paschalidis
